OL,3,CJust Stop Oil protesters jailed for
OL,4,Cconspiracy to block M25
OL,6,FJust Stop Oil protestors, including
OL,7,Fone of its co-founders, have been
OL,8,Fjailed for conspiring to organise
OL,9,Fprotests that blocked the M25 motorway.
OL,11,FFive protestors - Roger Hallam, 58,
OL,12,Ffrom Wales, Daniel Shaw, 38, from
OL,13,FNorthampton, Louise Lancaster, 58,
OL,14,Ffrom Cambridge, Lucia Whittaker De
OL,15,FAbreu, 35, from Derby and Cressida
OL,16,FGethin, 22, from Hereford - agreed to
OL,17,Fcause disruption to traffic by having
OL,18,Fprotesters climb onto gantries over
OL,19,Fthe motorway for four successive days
OL,20,Fin November 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
