OL,3,CJust Stop Oil protesters jailed for
OL,4,Cconspiracy to block M25
OL,6,FHallam, co-founder of Just Stop Oil
OL,7,Fand Extinction Rebellion, was
OL,8,Fsentenced to five years' imprisonment
OL,9,Fwhile the remaining four defendants
OL,10,Fwere each handed four years'
OL,11,Fimprisonment.
OL,13,FIt comes as three airports have been
OL,14,Fgranted legal orders which ban climate
OL,15,Factivists from their sites.
OL,17,FThe protests led to an economic cost
OL,18,Fof at least #765,000, prosecutors
OL,19,Falleged, while the cost to the
OL,20,FMetropolitan Police was more than #1.1
OL,21,Fmillion.
