OL,3,CJust Stop Oil protesters jailed for
OL,4,Cconspiracy to block M25
OL,6,FMore than 50,000 hours of vehicle
OL,7,Fdelays were caused by the
OL,8,Fdemonstrations, which saw 45 people
OL,9,Fclimb up the gantries.
OL,11,FAn estimated 700,000 vehicles were
OL,12,Fimpacted on the M25, which was
OL,13,Fcompromised for more than 120 hours.
OL,15,FA police officer suffered concussion
OL,16,Fand bruising after being knocked off
OL,17,Fhis motorbike in traffic caused by one
OL,18,Fof the protests on November 9, 2022,
OL,19,Fprosecutor Jocelyn Ledward KC said at
OL,20,Fthe sentencing hearing, at Southwark
OL,21,FCrown Court, on Thursday.
