OL,3,CJust Stop Oil protesters jailed for
OL,4,Cconspiracy to block M25
OL,6,FAll five defendants, who were referred
OL,7,Fto as the Whole Truth Five by Just
OL,8,FStop Oil on social media, joined a
OL,9,FZoom call on November 2, 2022.
OL,11,FDiscussions were held during the call
OL,12,Fabout the planned protests, based off
OL,13,F"what was said expressly and what
OL,14,Fcould be inferred", with attempts made
OL,15,Fto recruit others for the protests on
OL,16,Fthe call, Ms Ledward told the court.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
