OL,3,CJust Stop Oil protesters jailed for
OL,4,Cconspiracy to block M25
OL,6,FA journalist from the Sun newspaper,
OL,7,Fwho had joined the call pretending to
OL,8,Fbe interested in the protest, managed
OL,9,Fto record some of it and passed the
OL,10,Frecordings on to the police.
OL,12,FJudge Christopher Hehir said the Zoom
OL,13,Fcall showed "how intricately planned
OL,14,Fthe disruption was and the
OL,15,Fsophistication involved", and was
OL,16,F"compelling evidence" of the existence
OL,17,Fof a conspiracy.
