OL,6,FThere was "extensive organisation and
OL,7,Fplanning" for the protests and each
OL,8,Fdefendant had a "significant role" in
OL,9,Fthe conspiracy, Ms Ledward said.
OL,11,FThe defendants were convicted by a
OL,12,Fjury of conspiracy intentionally to
OL,13,Fcause a public nuisance, contrary to
OL,14,Fsection 78 of the Police, Crime,
OL,15,FSentencing and Courts Act 2022 and
OL,16,FSection 1 of the Criminal Law Act
OL,17,F1977, on July 11.
