OL,6,FThe defendants spoke to confirm their
OL,7,Fnames in court and shouted "We love
OL,8,Fyou" from the dock immediately after
OL,9,Fthe sentences were passed down.
OL,11,FJudge Hehir said: "The plain fact is
OL,12,Fthat each of you some time ago has
OL,13,Fcrossed the line from concerned
OL,14,Fcampaigner to fanatic.
OL,16,F"You have appointed yourselves as sole
OL,17,Farbiters of what should be done about
OL,18,Fclimate change."
