OL,6,FAddressing Hallam, the judge said:
OL,7,F"You are the theoretician, the 'ideas'
OL,8,Fman.
OL,10,F"In my judgment you sit at the very
OL,11,Fhighest level of the conspiracy."
OL,13,FThe judge told the court that 11
OL,14,Fprotesters were arrested on suspicion
OL,15,Fof contempt outside the court during
OL,16,Fthe case's trial on July 2, but the
OL,17,Fcourt had discontinued its proceedings
OL,18,Fagainst them on July 11 after he
OL,19,Fbecame "concerned" about their
OL,20,Fposition.
